node.text: It’s no secret that we enjoy modeling but what makes it even more fun for us is getting to work with a brand we truly love! #ad We thought it would be fun to give you guys a small glimpse into our life with some behind-the-scenes footage from our latest shoot with @americangirlbrand  and their NEWEST Fashion Show Collection! This shoot was probably one of our favorite shoots to date! We LOVE the matching Athleisure Wear for both dolls and girls! If you haven’t had a chance to check out the FULL collection- click on the link in our bio! #MyAmericanGirl

node.title: Behind the scenes with Us, American Girl, & their NEW Athleisure Mix & Matc

node.text: In case you guys missed it, we had the honor of introducing Kira Bailey - The American Girl Doll of the year for 2021 a few days ago, along with our Dad. Kira comes with some of the cutest pets and accessories we have ever seen! If you haven’t had a chance to see them all, you can check them out here! http://bit.ly/37ZbApz

node.title: We had SO MUCH FUN unveiling the 2021 @americangirlbrand GOTY- Kira 🐨🦘

node.text:
We’ve been looking for FUN new activities to do during Covid and our mom thought it would be fun to try Stand Up Paddleboarding! We don’t have much room in our garage to store anything else so she come across these AWESOME inflatable SUP sets! Each set comes with a board, paddle, and pump and fits inside a backpack so we can easily store them and take them to and from the beach inside our car. Today was our first time ever trying them on our own and we had the BEST time! Can’t wait to get out on the water again soon! Check out this little video our mom made and see if we ended up staying dry or falling off 🤪
Oh and you can check out https://bit.ly/3cIGiDL and get 10% off all products + FREE Shipping in the US until Oct 31, 2020 11:59 pm on SereneLife using our code- CLEMENTS10

node.text: We are SO excited about this book!!! Our friend and photographer @joannebarratt_photo is coming out with a new inspirational guide for young women!  She interviewed 100 different women doing 100 different jobs all over the country who each gave insightful ideas and words of wisdom from their experiences to help the next generation of girls find something they love to do! We love this idea and and may even know someone personally inside this book (our mom 🥰). Check out the link in our bio today and help support her amazing book on Kickstarter!!

node.text: One of our favorite things about visiting the east coast is getting to spend time with our cousin Shane 💙 Even though Shanes’s only 3 years old, he is our hero 💪🏼 When he was around 6 months old he was diagnosed with Spinal Muscular Atrophy… but that doesn’t stop him from fighting and working hard to get stronger everyday. We love him soooooooo much 🥰 Swipe left to see our little superhero in action 🦸🏻‍♂️ @nevergiveuporg #stronglikeshane
